[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "line": 14,
    "target_en": "Shion Sonozaki's last confession is dubious."
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "line": 20,
    "target_en": "Did the hag convince her that the Sonozaki family had nothing to do with it?"
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "line": 25,
    "target_en": "Or is that the truth?"
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "line": 31,
    "target_en": "In my own investigations so far, I've proven there are aspects of the curse which can't be explained by the Sonozaki family alone."
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "line": 37,
    "target_en": "So, my notes were all bogus from the beginning."
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "line": 42,
    "target_en": "These two hundred pages are full of bullshit."
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "line": 48,
    "target_en": "I thought of burning this notebook."
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "line": 54,
    "target_en": "But I won't do it."
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "line": 59,
    "target_en": "This notebook proves my guilt."
  },
  {
    "id": 10,
    "line": 64,
    "target_en": "I won't distort the facts."
  },
  {
    "id": 11,
    "line": 69,
    "target_en": "I won't burn it."
  },
  {
    "id": 12,
    "line": 75,
    "target_en": "After all, my life was only a notebook long."
  },
  {
    "id": 13,
    "line": 81,
    "target_en": "I wonder if anybody will read this."
  },
  {
    "id": 14,
    "line": 87,
    "target_en": "If somebody does, please let them learn something from my stupidity."
  },
  {
    "id": 15,
    "line": 93,
    "target_en": "The series of mysterious deaths in Hinamizawa..."
  },
  {
    "id": 16,
    "line": 98,
    "target_en": "Dubbed 'Oyashiro-sama's curse.'"
  },
  {
    "id": 17,
    "line": 104,
    "target_en": "If you're reading this..."
  },
  {
    "id": 18,
    "line": 109,
    "target_en": "...Please find the truth."
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "line": 115,
    "target_en": "That's"
